A Vagrant Environment to easily boot up a VM running BardCanvas

$ git clone https://github.com/mindful-zd/vagrant-bardcanvas.git
$ cd vagrant-bardcanvas/
$ vagrant up

Then go to: 
https://localhost:8016/

Accept the self signed certificate security exception, then login with the following credentials:
username: admin
password: admin

Alternatively, on your terminal:

$ vagrant ssh
$ cd /public_html

and hack away
